      "title_zh": "安全研究员对 CVE-2026-48710 漏洞进行大规模扫描，发现互联网中存在大量 API 密钥泄露风险",
      "title_orig": "RT Markus Vervier: The team did some data analysis on CVE-2026-48710 on a sample of 50.000 scanned hosts on the Internet. Spoiler: Lots of API keys ar...",
